data.description: Montaro 4 model built by Minto at PortoSol includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2nd floor loft, gorgeous kitchen, salt water filtered pool with custom outdoor kitchen, bar and entertainment venue! The spacious kitchen includes new stainless appliances, granite, island, gas stove, decorative mosaic tile back splash and counter lighting. The house was freshly painted on the inside and fresh vinyl flooring on the entire second floor.  Other features include accordion shutters, crown molding, fans throughout the home and family room , tinted windows, Concrete added between floor to minimize noise. PortoSol includes resort style pool, professionally equipped fitness center, billiards room, outdoor basketball and tennis courts, multi-station fitness trail, 100 acres of lakes, greenery and recreation.
